# [OPSAREA](../wg/opsarea.html)

## Summary

The OPSAREA session at IETF 125, chaired by Mahesh Jethanandani and Mohamed (Med) Boucadair, covered the state of the Operations and Management Area, including updates from the GROW and SRV6OPS working groups. A significant portion of the meeting was dedicated to the workload and challenges of the YANG Doctors, progress on the revision of the operations and management guidelines (`draft-ietf-opsawg-rfc5706bis`), and a series of guest presentations regarding AI-driven operations (AIOps) from major network operators. The session concluded with a report on the DNS@IETF considerations regarding the future structure of DNS-related work within the IETF.

